---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="Performance Testing">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-tachometer"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Performance Engineering from Day One</h3>
          <p>Rayinfos Technologies begins performance tests at the development phase itself, not at the end — so bottlenecks are found and fixed in context, not after thousands of lines of code have accumulated. Our four-step methodology covers strategy, simulation, analysis and tuning.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-flag-checkered"></i></div>
            <h5>Pre-launch Testing</h5>
            <p>Pre-launch performance measuring and tuning to ensure your application is production-ready before it goes live.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-bolt"></i></div>
            <h5>Load &amp; Baseline Testing</h5>
            <p>Baseline and load testing under simulated real-world traffic conditions, including scalability, reliability and failover scenarios.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-fire"></i></div>
            <h5>Stress Testing</h5>
            <p>Reliability, scalability and stress testing to discover how your application behaves when pushed beyond normal operating conditions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-bug"></i></div>
            <h5>Bottleneck Analysis</h5>
            <p>Precise identification and resolution of performance bottlenecks using CPU/RAM, heap memory and thread contention metrics.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-line-chart"></i></div>
            <h5>Metrics &amp; Reporting</h5>
            <p>Comprehensive client-side and server-side monitoring with performance benchmarking and detailed metrics reporting.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-wrench"></i></div>
            <h5>Performance Tuning</h5>
            <p>Fix bottlenecks, validate changes and verify that performance targets are met — improving application responsiveness without hardware upgrades.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
